reviewText: It's very funny.... HE'S very funny.  I felt like I was there and laughing with him when he'd crack up.  I miss Mr. Varney so much.  He died too young.  I have tried to find this on DVD but I guess it doesn't exist.  I already own it on VHS.  He does a whole lot of commercials for many items, each several times over....  SO funny!
